title: LEXANI WHEELS: "The Beast" 750HP REZURXN Challenger Teaser
description:
Click subscribe for new videos weekly!

Watch in 1080p HD!

LEXANI.COM

Modified Dodge Challenger
Special thanks to K&N Filters, Magnaflow, Gilles Marini, and Exotics Racing Las Vegas.

22" LS-101 Custom Paint Finish 

Engine Mods;
6.2 Hemi engine with Procharged induction, large fuel rail, large injectors, API Fuel Pump, Comp Cam, Comp Pushrods and Comp Cam Spring Kit with Comp Cam Titanium Spring Retainers, Auto Meter gauges, Methanol injection, Custom Cerakote Methanol reservoir, Fluidyne Aluminum Radiator, Custom Cerakote Over Flow reservoir, Long tube headers with X pipe and MagnaFlow mufflers.

Vehicle Mods:
 Custom Lexani 22" rims and tires, Eibach Pro R2 Suspension, Front Strut support, Custom Silicone Hoses, Oracle Halo lighting, (inside and out), Blacked out headlights, tail lights, marker lights, grill and emblems, with custom Tint.
